强制企业统一采购测温仪？仙桃官方回应。
Mandatory Corporate Procurement of Thermometer? Andromeda Official Response.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 邓雅菲 实习生 陈紫嘉针对网传“仙桃100人以上企业均要安装红外线测温仪”一事，仙桃市新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎防控指挥部综合协调组具体负责人周冰峰2月22日回复澎湃新闻（www.thepaper.cn）称，网上传的《关于定购联通热成像人体测温设备的函》内容属实，但仙桃市并未强制要求100人以上的企业安装统一采购的红外线测温仪，只是向人数超过100人的复工企业推荐采购红外线测温仪，由复工企业自愿采购红外线测温仪或采取其它安全的解决方案。
Peng Pai reporter Deng Yafei intern Chen Zijia online for "more than 100 enterprises should install infrared thermometers," Xiantao City's new-style coronavirus infection of the Pneumonia Integrated Coordination Unit, said Sunday (www.thepaper.cn), but Xiantao did not force more than 100 people to install a unified infrared thermometer.
此前，一则“紧急通知”当天在网络流传，该通知称，“接仙桃市指挥部紧急通知，凡是100人以上的企业，无论当前复工与否，均要安装红外线测温仪，由市统一采购，价格9万左右”。
Earlier, a notice circulated on the Internet on the same day, saying: "Xiantao Formation Command emergency notice that 100 or more enterprises, regardless of whether or not the current resumption of work, will be installed infrared thermometer, by the city unified procurement, prices around 90,000."
一则“紧急通知”在网络流传。
An "emergency notice" circulated on the Internet.
与此通知相关的，则是周冰峰提到内容属实的函件《关于定购联通热成像人体测温设备的函》。
Related to this notice is Zhou Bingfeng refers to the true content of the letter "Order Unicom Thermal Imaging Human Temperature Equipment Letter."
这份函件此前也在网络流传，显示为仙桃市新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎防控指挥部发布。
This letter has also been circulated in the network, showing that the new coronavirus infection in Xiantao City, the Pneumonia Command issued.
这份函件提到，“仙桃市新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎防控指挥部决定向你公司订购‘热成像人体测温系统’22套，每套单价为8.5万元以内（包安装）。
"The Pneumonia Prevention and Control Command for the new coronavirus infection in Xiantao has decided to place an order with your company for 22 sets of Thermal Imaging Human Temperature Detection System (TIPS) with a unit price of less than 85,000 yuan per set (including installation).
”一则仙桃市新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎防控指挥部《关于定购联通热成像人体测温设备的函》在网络流传。
A letter from the Pneumonia Prevention and Control Bureau of Xiantao's new coronavirus infection "Letter on Ordering Unicom Thermal Imaging Human Thermal Imaging Equipment" circulated on the Internet.
“通知下传出现失误，是推荐而非强制企业采购”“我们从来没有强制要求企业采购红外线测温仪，可能是在我们企业生产组在向乡镇发通知后，乡镇联系企业时传达信息有误。
"We've never made it mandatory for companies to buy infrared thermometers, probably because our production team miscommunicated when they contacted companies after they notified the townships.
了解到这个情况后，我已向市委常委、统战部部长和企业生产组负责人报告了这一情况，并安排了专人向企业做解释工作。
With this in mind, I have reported the situation to the Municipal Standing Committee, the Head of the Operations Department and the Head of the Enterprise Production Group, and have arranged for an explanation to be given to the enterprise.
”周冰峰说。
"said Zhou.
周冰峰进一步解释说，作为全国的防护物资生产基地，仙桃市每天必须完成4.5万套防护服的生产量，目前有相当多的企业面临着复工复产，所以向人数超过100人的复工企业推荐采购红外线测温仪，由复工企业自愿采购红外线测温仪或采取其它安全的解决方案。
Zhou further explained that Xiantao, the national base for the production of protective equipment, must produce 45,000 sets of protective clothing every day. A considerable number of enterprises are facing the task of resuming production, so infrared thermometers are recommended for enterprises with more than 100 workers.
“此外，由于红外线测温仪属于市场上紧缺的资源，需要提前定货，所以仙桃市政府才考虑代为收集企业需求信息，统计后，交由联通、电信、移动等3家运营商提前订购，并抓紧安装，利用高科技设备确保企业安全生产。
"In addition, because infrared thermometers are a scarce resource on the market and require advance orders, the city government is considering collecting information on demand from companies and then placing them with three operators, including Unicom, Telecom and Mobile, to order in advance and install them quickly, using high-tech equipment to ensure safe production.
”周冰峰说。
"said Zhou.
仙桃市目前对复工的企业有明确的要求，必须要有专班负责抓、有防护应急物资、有分时段防护记录、有人车出入检测记载、有复工前消毒措施、有员工健康体检报告。
Xiantao enterprises now have clear requirements for the resumption of work, there must be special classes responsible for grasp, emergency protection materials, time-limited protection records, car access records, pre-work disinfection measures, staff health examination reports.
“基于安全防护措施的考量，政府才向企业推荐了红外线测温仪。
"It is because of safety precautions that the government has recommended infrared thermometers to companies.
如果企业使用其他满足条件的设备，不管是红外线测温仪，还是手持体温枪，只要能确保企业安全生产，我们都是允许复工的。
If companies use other equipment that meets their requirements, be it infrared thermometers or hand-held thermostats, we are allowed to go back to work as long as it ensures safe production.
”周冰峰说。
"said Zhou.
“采购红外线测温仪有难度，很难短时间抢到货”据周冰峰介绍，2月8日，仙桃市新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎防控指挥部综合协调组曾向湖北省各地市州咨询，得知大部分地市州都向中国联通定购过红外线测温仪，全省价格均为8.5万元。
The integrated coordination group of the Pneumonia Prevention and Control Command for the new coronavirus infection in Xiantao consulted with cities and counties throughout Hubei Province and learned that most of them had ordered infra-red thermometers from China Unicom, at a price of 85,000 yuan, said Zhou.
周冰峰说，订购函提到的22套红外线测温仪，其中21套由政府出资采购，1套由仙桃市某重点物资保障商超采购。
Zhou said 22 sets of infrared thermometers mentioned in the order were purchased by the government and one by a key material supplier in Xiantao City.
政府采购的21套设备中有10套运用于仙桃市重点定点医院，11套用于保障全省医用防护服生产的11家定点企业和配套企业。
Ten of the 21 sets of equipment procured by the government were used in key designated hospitals in Xiantao City and 11 designated enterprises and supporting enterprises for the production of medical protective clothing throughout the province.
由于测温仪器紧缺，截至2月22日，仍有两套未到货。
Two sets of undelivered items remained as at 22 February owing to a shortage of temperature measuring instruments.
“我们现在采购红外线测温仪都有难度，即使是电信、联通、移动三家运营商加起来，都很难短时间抢购到货。
"We now have difficulty procuring infrared thermometers, and even three operators, telecommunications, connectivity and mobile, have trouble snapping up shipments in a short time.
”周冰峰说。
"said Zhou.
